      <content:encoded><![CDATA[<h1>The Linden Method</h1>
<p><object width="500" height="306"><param name="movie" value="http://www.youtube.com/v/48Qr37DzHlA?version=3"></param><param name="allowFullScreen" value="true"></param><param name="allowscriptaccess" value="always"></param><embed src="http://www.youtube.com/v/48Qr37DzHlA?version=3" type="application/x-shockwave-flash" width="500" height="306" allowscriptaccess="always" allowfullscreen="true"></embed></object></p>
<h3><em><em><em><em><a href="http://www.overcomingpanicattackstoday.com/thelindenmethod">Click Here Now To Visit The Official Linden Method Site.</a></em></em></em></em></h3>
<p>The above video above features Charles Linden the creator of the Linden method at a keynote speech. This method as he explains is the structure around the method where he treated himself after 25 years of suffering, quickly and permanently.
<p>
He was suffering from Anxiety, Panic Attacks, OCD. He had tried many treatments such as prescribed medication, alternative methods and P to name but a few, but nothing worked.</p>
<p>For most sufferers, a panic attack  can apparently come  from  nowhere. Their symptoms can feel as though they are having a heart  attack with actual chest pains symptoms. It&#8217;s always important to have  these type of symptoms checked out by a doctor.</p>
<p>If the sufferer finds that they have to start to perform rituals to  help stop the panic attacks, then they have developed obsessive  compulsive disorder or ocd.  The same type of treatment can be effective  for both ocd and panic attacks</p>
<p>Charles Linden then decided to take things into his own hands and find out why some people were cured off the problems he was suffering. From this the linden method was born.</p>
<p>Is it a scam. I do not think so. The man is genuine and the speech is to health professionals. It is hard not to be moved by the testimonials on the video and  I would ask you to look out for the one by Lucy Barton.</p>
<p><em><strong>Comment on Youtube </strong>- &#8220;Hi Im lee pearce &amp; I used your method 2 years ago &amp; saw a  vast improvement in my condition. I went from house bound 2 back 2 work  in months when I realised how harmless anxiety really is. I learnt  guitar in the process of my recovery &amp; have recently set up on my  own gigging &amp; just returned from the national rock idol final in  scotland. Impossible before u used the method. carry on the good work.  Through the Internet I have helped many friends that also suffered. Take  care <img src='http://www.overcomingpanicattackstoday.com/wp-includes/images/smilies/icon_wink.gif' alt=';-)' class='wp-smiley' /> &#8221;</em></p>
<p><strong>Lee Pearce</strong></p>
<p>The web site is scattered with other great testimonials and is endorsed by the medical professionals. There is also a<strong> risk free guarantee</strong>. With over 13 years in practice and <strong>well over 100,000 customers</strong>, I highly recommend the Linden method.</p>
<h3><em><em><em><em><a><em><em><em><em></em></em></em></em></a><em><em><em><em><a href="http://www.overcomingpanicattackstoday.com/thelindenmethod">Click Here Now To Visit The Official Linden Method Site.</a></em></em></em></em></em></em></em></em></h3>
]]></content:encoded>
